Xterminal v1.0.x
December 22, 2002
CREDITS: People that contributed on this project

Dragos Acostachioaie <dragos@biosfarm.ro>
	He elaborated it's concept and structure and written the foundation
	class, XObject, and other classes. He is also the current maintainer
	of the project.

Pavel Andreew <pavel@collage.etel.ru>
	Fixed lot of bugs, added XtComboBox

Sjoerd de Heer <s.a.deheer@student.utwente.nl>
	Added support for selecting a given number of elements in XtList

Bernd Kalbfuss <slice@t-online.de>
	Designed the event handling model and written parts of the
	documentation.

Ric Klaren <ia_ric@cs.utwente.nl>
	Written the hierarchical list class, XtHList

Udo Kreckel <udokre@gmx.de>
	Added multi-line and right-justified input fields, fixed lot of bugs.

Adrian Teohar <silconex@mail.dntis.ro>
	Written various classes and worked together with Dragos at the
	basically classes. Retired.

	Many other people contributed with bug reports, suggestions, ideas:

